    "TencentChinese": "合金金属",
    "TraditionalChinese": "合金"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Combined neutral alloy with uses that range from pharmacology all the way to heavy industry. Crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ionized Cobalt</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ammonia</span>.<br><br>Forms the backbone of galactic alloy trading.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用途极其广泛的中性合金，从医药到重工业都有它的用武之地。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">离子钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">氨</span>制作而成。<br><br>它是星系合金贸易的核心组成部分。",
    "TencentChinese": "用途极其广泛的中性合金，从医药到重工业都有它的用武之地。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">氯</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">氨</span>制作而成。<br><br>它是星系合金贸易的核心组成部分。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "混合而成的中性合金，用途極廣；從製藥到重工業等產業均會使用。以<span class=\"name name-earth\">離子化鈷</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">氨</span>製作而成。<br><br>是銀河系合金貿易的基石。"
  },
